---
/**
 * The page's one poster moment: the date, huge. Deliberately breaks the
 * index grammar (the only centered, oversized typographic outburst) per the
 * one-centered-moment rule. Content-light on purpose; the urgency is real.
 */
---

<section class="overflow-hidden border-y border-line" aria-label="Investor Day date">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 text-center md:py-28">
    <p class="reveal flex items-center justify-center gap-3 font-mono text-[0.75rem] tracking-[0.08em] text-fog">
      <span class="relative inline-flex size-2 rounded-full bg-phoenix-bright" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      cohort 2 · investor day
    </p>
    <p class="reveal mt-4 font-display text-[clamp(4.5rem,14vw,11rem)] leading-none tracking-[-0.02em] text-paper">
      July <em class="text-phoenix-bright">31.</em>
    </p>
    <p class="reveal mt-6 font-mono text-[0.8125rem] tracking-[0.08em] text-fog-dim">
      30 teams pitch 19 firms. then it is cohort 3's turn.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
